(413, '<p>Pricing your dishes should never be down to trial and error and the chef''s usually less than perfect assessment of market conditions. This is a beginner level spreadsheet to help you make some vital decisions right away.</p>\r\n<p>For those of you who really want to do it right, then we urge you to use the best menu and recipe costing tool in the business, <a title="Catercost" href="http://www.hospitalityentrepreneur.com.gridhosted.co.uk/index.php?cID=274">CaterCost</a></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><a href="/index.php/download_file/view/46/">Innventive_dish_costing_tool.xls</a></p>'),
