(299, '<h2>About Hospitality Entrepreneur</h2>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<div class="under-big-title"><strong>Welcome to Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE)</strong>, a new information and advice service for independent hospitality business owners. <br /><br />HE provides you with unique access to industry experts, content and resources to help you make your business more efficient and profitable. <br /><br />Our goal is to ensure that you get: <img src="http://hospitalityentrepreneur.com/member/images/about-he-image.png" alt="" align="right" />\r\n<ul class="list-better">\r\n<li>Better <strong>profits</strong></li>\r\n<li>Better <strong>knowledge</strong></li>\r\n<li>Better <strong>peace of mind</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<h6>How do we do this?</h6>\r\nWe are a collaboration of leading industry professionals and companies, with proven expertise in building successful hospitality businesses. <br /><br />Every month we will release the best and latest industry advice (see Resources) to our members. This will be available for your use as and when you want it, 24/7, ready for you and your staff to implement in your business. <br /><br />In addition to business advice, our members also enjoy privileged access to our Partner business services. <br /><br /><strong><em>Do you want to expand your business but dont know how?</em> </strong><br /><br /><strong><em>Would you like to radically increase your businesss profits whilst decreasing its reliance on YOU?</em> </strong><br /><br /><strong><em>Does your business control you, rather than the other way around?</em></strong> <br /><br />If the answer to any of these questions is yes, then you are a hospitality entrepreneur so join today.</div>\r\n<h5></h5>'),
(300, '<h1>Our Partners</h1>\r\n<p><span>A collaboration of tried and tested industry suppliers and professionals provide you with the best possible service. They have</span> <span><span>proven, unrivalled experience and expertise in supplying and running profitable hospitality businesses. Our Partners are driven by a shared vision for providing increased profitability, knowledge and peace of mind for our members. <br /><br />We are also in discussion with additional market leading companies and content providers, with the aim of making Hospitality Entrepreneur unquestionably beneficial to our membership. </span></span></p>'),
(309, '<h1>Membership</h1>\r\n<p><span><strong>So, why join?</strong><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span>The most cost-effective way to take advantage of all that Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE) has to offer is to join as an HE ''Starter'' member. <br /><br />Not only do you get access to every publication we produce, now and in the future, you benefit from a range of exclusive services that you simply cant get at a better price anywhere else. <br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<p></p>'),
