(892, '<h1 class="home centered"><span>Solutions for smarter hospitality <br /></span></h1>\r\n<p class="centered textPad">It''s like having your own personal industry expert with you full time, but without having to pay the expensive day rate. As a ground breaking new collaboration of proven industry experts and companies, we can ensure you get better profits, better knowledge and better peace of mind.</p>\r\n<h3 class="centered textPad">Here''s what we''ve got for you:</h3>\r\n<div class="grid-6 column">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>24/7 advice and success ''secrets'' from entrepreneurs and hospitality business owners, like you, to provide expert guidance to hospitality business owners, like you!</li>\r\n<li>inspiration, exclusive insights, practical help, 1:1 mentoring</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grid-6 column">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>a real chance to control and grow your business before it controls you</li>\r\n<li>years of combined knowledge, experience and systems gift-wrapped for you</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>'),
(897, ' <div class="grid-3 columns formimage">\r\n        	<img src="/files/3213/9600/3699/Free-30-day-trial.png" alt="Hospitality Entrepreneur FREE Trial"/>\r\n        </div>\r\n        \r\n        <div class="grid-9 columns formIntro">\r\n        	<h2>Enjoy Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE) FREE for 30 days</h2>\r\n            <p>Gain access to at least 70% of the HE website, test drive our Member benefits and resources, be among the first to hear about our launch news and benefit from being a part of our growing Club </p>\r\n\r\n<a href="/membership/free-trial/" class="bigButt darkButt">Get your FREE 30 day trial NOW</a>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n            </div>'),
(901, '<h1 style="text-align: center;">YOUR FREE TRIAL</h1>\r\n<h3><strong>KNOWLEDGE:</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>24/7 access to at least 70% of downloadable HE website member advice and business resources</li>\r\n<li>Members Only business building blogs from our editors and Partners</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>PEACE OF MIND:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Your own Business Health Check questionnaire</li>\r\n<li>Templates, checklists and systems to start using in your business today</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>PROFIT:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Exclusive access and unique deals with our Partner business services</li>\r\n<li>Ready-to-use profit boosting strategies</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>and instant access to a treasure chest of proven hospitality marketing and operations nuggets including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Marketing :</strong> the latest hospitality marketing tips, online and offline trends and best practices</li>\r\n<li><strong>Exclusive HE videos :</strong> hospitality how-to, in weekly released videos from industry top performers</li>\r\n<li><strong>Entrepreneur skills :</strong> everything you need to start controlling and growing your business TODAY</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align="center"><strong>Register Now (It''s Free)</strong></p>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class="grid-10 columns nopadLeft">\r\n<h4>In addition to receiving your FREE copy of the Sunday Times bestseller Bottys Rules (RRP 12.99) in the post*, when you claim your free Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE) 30 day trial, youll get a taste of our exclusive members benefits:</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grid-2 columns nopadRight"><img src="{CCM:FID_143}" alt="bottyrules.jpg" width="180" height="288" /></div>'),
(902, '<div class="disclaimer">\r\n<p><strong>PAYMENT DETAILS:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Note: You will be asked to provide payment details before your 30 day FREE trial starts. Once you register, youll have continuous access to the HE members website via the username and password you choose. Well also send you brief announcements when new content is posted. As always, we respect your privacy, and you can unsubscribe at any time. Whats more, if you are not entirely happy during your first 30 days, you can unsubscribe and you will not be charged a penny, dime, yen or whatever your chosen currency.</p>\r\n<p>Youll also receive HUMAN induction and welcome calls from both Peter Austen (HE founder) and our partners at Nigel Botterills Entrepreneurs Circle during your 300 day trial.</p>\r\n<p>In other words, by signing up right now, and putting into practice what youll learn, youll soon join the ranks of some of the smartest hospitality pros on the planet.</p>\r\n</div>'),
