(390, ' <div class="grid-3 columns formimage">\r\n        	<img src="/files/5313/9282/1743/free_book.png" alt=""/>\r\n        </div>\r\n        \r\n        <div class="grid-5 columns formIntro">\r\n        	<h2>Start beating your competition</h2>\r\n            <p>Claim your free, exclusive e-book written by our Partners at the Entrepreneurs Circle, The 7 Golden Rules of Profitable Restaurant Marketing, worth 9.99, and be the first to hear about our launch news and how you can join Hospitality Business Growth Club.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n            \r\n            \r\n<div class="grid-4 columns guideForm">\r\n            \r\n                        <form accept-charset="UTF-8" action="https://vn172.infusionsoft.com/app/form/process/a009de1a3568bc0f35eacacce1d68480" class="infusion-form" method="POST">\r\n    <input name="inf_form_xid" type="hidden" value="a009de1a3568bc0f35eacacce1d68480" />\r\n    <input name="inf_form_name" type="hidden" value="FREE ebook" />\r\n    <input name="infusionsoft_version" type="hidden" value="1.29.10.21" />\r\n\r\n        <input class="watermark" id="inf_field_FirstName" name="inf_field_FirstName" type="text" placeholder="Name *" />\r\n\r\n        <input class="watermark" id="inf_field_Email" name="inf_field_Email" type="text" placeholder="Email *"/>\r\n\r\n    <input type="submit" value="Get your FREE e-book now" class="formSubmitButton" />    \r\n\r\n</form>\r\n            \r\n</div>\r\n'),
(904, '<h1 style="text-align: left;">YOUR FREE TRIAL</h1>\r\n<h3><strong>KNOWLEDGE:</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>24/7 access to at least 70% of downloadable HE website member advice and business resources</li>\r\n<li>Members Only business building blogs from our editors and Partners</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>PEACE OF MIND:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Your own Business Health Check questionnaire</li>\r\n<li>Templates, checklists and systems to start using in your business today</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>PROFIT:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Exclusive access and unique deals with our Partner business services</li>\r\n<li>Ready-to-use profit boosting strategies</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>and instant access to a treasure chest of proven hospitality marketing and operations nuggets including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Marketing :</strong> the latest hospitality marketing tips, online and offline trends and best practices</li>\r\n<li><strong>Exclusive HE videos :</strong> hospitality how-to, in weekly released videos from industry top performers</li>\r\n<li><strong>Entrepreneur skills :</strong> everything you need to start controlling and growing your business TODAY</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align="center"><strong>Register Now (It''s Free)</strong></p>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class="grid-10 columns nopadLeft">\r\n<h4>In addition to receiving your FREE copy of the Sunday Times bestseller Bottys Rules (RRP 12.99) in the post*, when you claim your free Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE) 30 day trial, youll get a taste of our exclusive members benefits:</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grid-2 columns nopadRight"><img src="{CCM:FID_143}" alt="bottyrules.jpg" width="180" height="288" /></div>'),
(393, '<div class="row membersSignUp">\r\n<h4 id="plussideintro"><strong>Subscribe to Hospitality Entrepreneur</strong></h4>\r\n<p>Premium content that helps you make the right decisions, take the right actions, and focus on what really matters.</p>\r\n<div class="grid-4 columns">\r\n<h3>option 1</h3>\r\n<p>Text about option</p>\r\n<a class="signButt" href="#">Sign Up</a></div>\r\n<div class="grid-4 columns">\r\n<h3>option 2</h3>\r\n<p>Text about option</p>\r\n<a class="signButt" href="#">Sign Up</a></div>\r\n<div class="grid-4 columns">\r\n<h3>option 3</h3>\r\n<p>Text about option</p>\r\n<a class="signButt" href="#">Sign Up</a></div>\r\n</div>'),
(394, '<h3>Articles, blogs, checklists and numerous trade secrets</h3>\r\n<p><img src="http://hospitalityentrepreneur.com/member/images/about-partners/partners-pics.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>from left to right: <strong>Andrew Pring, Carol Emmas, Peter Austen, Ali Carter and Nigel Botterill</strong></p>\r\n<p>A sprinkling of the hottest advice and help is provided by our assortment of writers and business experts.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Andrew Pring</strong>, our Business Editor has plenty to say on the business issues that are constantly changing the hospitality sector. With experience as editor at the Licensee &amp; Morning Advertiser and BII Business, he knows a fair bit about the pub industry especially. Also, <strong>Carol Emmas </strong>joins us from a recent stint as taste editor at Harpers Wine &amp; Spirit trade review when shes not writing for numerous hospitality publications.</p>\r\n<p>Insight and inspiration is provided by one of the countrys best known serial entrepreneurs, <strong>Nigel Botterill</strong>. He knows a fair bit about starting, expanding and selling multi-million pound businesses, having done that himself from scratch six (at the last count!) times in the last eight years.</p>\r\n<p>Practical operational advice, including checklists, templates and behind the scenes insights is also provide by <strong>Peter Austen</strong> and <strong>Ali Carter</strong>, who have all the war stories and overview necessary after owning and running a variety of super-successful restaurants, hotels, pubs and bars themselves.</p>'),
(395, '<div class="member-benefit">\r\n<h3>Join Today</h3>\r\n<p>Join today using your exclusive 25% OFF VIP Launch Offer available to those who complete our <a href="http://hospitalityentrepreneur.com/survey.html">2 minute survey</a></p>\r\n<ul class="span5">\r\n<li>Attract and KEEP more customers</li>\r\n<li>Increase your bottom line profits</li>\r\n<li>Access exclusive member business resources 24/7</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class="span7">\r\n<li>Access easy-to-implement business growth secrets</li>\r\n<li>Benefit from the latest marketing, training and legal support</li>\r\n<li>Start implementing and benefitting, or your money back</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Subscribe for as little as 9.95 (plus VAT) per month or pay an annual subscription in one go for 119.40 (plus VAT) and enjoy 3 months extra for FREE</p>\r\n</div>'),
