(411, '<h1>Entrepreneurs Circle</h1>\r\n<h4>The UKs Largest Membership Organisation Dedicated to Helping Business Grow</h4>\r\n<p><span>In the last 8 years Nigel Botterill has built 8 separate 1m businesses from scratch, so he knows a thing or two about business growth. Nigels Entrepreneurs Circle is the UKs largest membership organisation dedicated to helping business grow. With a national network of Business Growth Advisors (BGAs) and 130 local meetings each month across the UK, thousands of entrepreneurs have been helped by discovering new ideas and then making them work in their own businesses. Now we have joined forces to launch a business advice and ''done for you'' marketing service tailored for hospitality.</span><br /><br /><span>All Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE) ''Starter'' members gain marketing and business growth advice and tips from Nigel and his advisors from Day 1, posted regularly on our website and blogs. Whilst Starter subscription to HE does not include membership of the Entrepreneurs Circle, you can qualify for preferential and exclusive joining fees, especially for the new Club Plus membership level which we are launching in March.</span><br /><br /><span>See our Membership page to find out how you can join Nigels Entrepreneurs Circle and have automatic exclusive access to his Club Plus Membership (usually 299 per month) and an additional marketing and business growth package that has been tailored to our industry.</span></p>'),
