(426, '<h1>Pelican</h1>\r\n<p>Whilst saving money is one of the benefits of becoming an HE member, Pelican also offer unique additional services as part of our Food Profit Club, including regular impartial tendering on your behalf, centralised billing and co-ordination with Catercost and Innventive, to help ensure you have the best possible ongoing controls on your food costings and profits.</p>\r\n<p>Pelican also lead the way in negotiating utility bills, chemicals, disposable, janitorial, credit &amp; debit card processing and catering equipment. In fact, most areas of running a hospitality business!</p>'),
(427, '<h1>Pelican Procurement Services</h1>\r\n<h4>Group purchasing power and efficiency through outourced procurement and invoice management</h4>\r\n<p><span>By using Pelicans total collective purchasing volume of 140m, Hospitality Entrepreneur members are able to benefit from highly competitive trading arrangements with local and national suppliers, making substantial savings that would otherwise be unobtainable.</span></p>\r\n<p>Whilst saving money is one of the benefits of becoming an HE member, Pelican also offer unique additional services as part of our Food Profit Club, including regular impartial tendering on your behalf, centralised billing and co-ordination with Catercost and Innventive, to help ensure you have the best possible ongoing controls on your food costings and profits.</p>\r\n<p>Pelican also lead the way in negotiating utility bills, chemicals, disposable, janitorial, credit &amp; debit card processing and catering equipment. In fact, most areas of running a hospitality business!</p>'),
(428, '<p>Partners Resources to go here</p>'),
(431, '<h1>ABV Training</h1>\r\n<p>ABV Training is an award winning company and leading provider of fun and effective personal license training (APLH (formerley NCPLH) &amp; SCPLH ) and other BIIAB, HABC and CIEH qualifications at venues across the UK. Approved providers of the Apprenticeship in Licensed Hospitality for both Level 2 and 3, they also offer a wide range of affordable e-courses suitable for consistent induction and compliance training.</p>\r\n<p>Recognised as one of the very top training providers, they work for many of the UK''s leading operators in pubs, hotels and leisure offering bespoke courses tailored to meet business needs. David and Frazer and their team based across the country offer such a comprehensive training solution that it would have been crazy not to have teamed up with Hospitality Entrepreneur, to provide you and your staff team with all the back up and qualifications you need!</p>'),
(435, '<h1>Cater Coast</h1>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>Helping independent food operators squeeze every last drop of profit from their business and live the happy lives they deserve. Thats Catercosts mission.</p>\r\n<p>Knowing how hard it can be to know down to the last penny, the cost of the food you make and sell on your menu, this makes it easy, freeing you to cook while Catercost crunches your numbers!</p>\r\n<p>Features include:</p>\r\n<p> Cloud technology<br /> No software to download<br /> Recipe and menu creation<br /> Food profit calculator<br /> Nutritional information<br /> Supplier comparison on ingredients</p>\r\n<p>Club members of HE can have automatic use of Catercost, whilst Ali Carters sound and straight talking advice is available to all members.</p>'),
(436, '<h1>Cater Coast</h1>\r\n<h4>Online recipe and menu costing</h4>\r\n<p><span>Catercost is a leading recipe costing and food profit calculator with nutritional info for caterers. Multi award winning licensee and trainer, Ali Carter set up Catercost to help the catering industry beat the statistics, take control and have a healthier business.</span></p>\r\n<p>Helping independent food operators squeeze every last drop of profit from their business and live the happy lives they deserve. Thats Catercosts mission.</p>\r\n<p>Knowing how hard it can be to know down to the last penny, the cost of the food you make and sell on your menu, this makes it easy, freeing you to cook while Catercost crunches your numbers!</p>\r\n<p>Features include:</p>\r\n<p> Cloud technology<br /> No software to download<br /> Recipe and menu creation<br /> Food profit calculator<br /> Nutritional information<br /> Supplier comparison on ingredients</p>\r\n<p>Club members of HE can have automatic use of Catercost, whilst Ali Carters sound and straight talking advice is available to all members.</p>'),
