(498, '<h1>Bond Dickson</h1>\r\n<h4>Group purchasing power and efficiency through outourced procurement and invoice management</h4>\r\n<p><span>By using Pelicans total collective purchasing volume of 140m, Hospitality Entrepreneur members are able to benefit from highly competitive trading arrangements with local and national suppliers, making substantial savings that would otherwise be unobtainable.</span></p>\r\n<p>Whilst saving money is one of the benefits of becoming an HE member, Pelican also offer unique additional services as part of our Food Profit Club, including regular impartial tendering on your behalf, centralised billing and co-ordination with Catercost and Innventive, to help ensure you have the best possible ongoing controls on your food costings and profits.</p>\r\n<p>Pelican also lead the way in negotiating utility bills, chemicals, disposable, janitorial, credit &amp; debit card processing and catering equipment. In fact, most areas of running a hospitality business!</p>'),
