(505, '<h1>Cater Cost</h1>\r\n<h4>Online recipe and menu costing</h4>\r\n<p><span>Catercost is a leading recipe costing and food profit calculator with nutritional info for caterers. Multi award winning licensee and trainer, Ali Carter set up Catercost to help the catering industry beat the statistics, take control and have a healthier business.</span></p>\r\n<p>Helping independent food operators squeeze every last drop of profit from their business and live the happy lives they deserve. Thats Catercosts mission.</p>\r\n<p>Knowing how hard it can be to know down to the last penny, the cost of the food you make and sell on your menu, this makes it easy, freeing you to cook while Catercost crunches your numbers!</p>\r\n<p>Features include:</p>\r\n<p> Cloud technology<br /> No software to download<br /> Recipe and menu creation<br /> Food profit calculator<br /> Nutritional information<br /> Supplier comparison on ingredients</p>\r\n<p>Club members of HE can have automatic use of Catercost, whilst Ali Carters sound and straight talking advice is available to all members.</p>'),
