(537, '<h3 class="home centered"><span>Solutions for Smarter Hospitality Marketing and Operating</span></h3>\r\n<p class="centered textPad">It''s like having your own personal industry expert with you full time but without having to pay the expensive day rate. As a ground breaking new collaboration of proven industry experts and companies, we can ensure you get better profits, better knowledge and better peace of mind.</p>\r\n<h3 class="centered textPad">Here''s what we''ve got for you:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>24/7 advice and success ''secrets'' from entrepreneurs and hospitality business owners, like you, to provide expert guidance to hospitality business owners, like you!</li>\r\n<li>a real chance to control and grow your business before it controls you</li>\r\n<li>inspiration, exclusive insights, practical help, 1:1 mentoring</li>\r\n<li>years of combined knowledge, experience and systems gift-wrapped for you</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(538, '<h3 class="home"><span>Who''s involved?</span> A total collaboration for you</h3>\r\n<p class="centered textPad">Leading industry suppliers and professionals bring proven, unrivalled experience and expertise in supplying and actually running profitable hospitality businesses. Our Partners are driven by a shared vision for providing increased profitability, knowledge and peace of mind for our members.</p>\r\n<p class="centered textPad"><span style="line-height: 115%;">The HE advisors and partners have already had the sleepless nights worrying about staff, premises and bills that need paying yesterday, so why not let them share their advice with you (theyve had their fair share of celebrations, financial successes</span> and Champagne popping also)?</p>'),
(539, ' <div class="grid-3 columns formimage">\r\n        	<img src="/files/5313/9282/1743/free_book.png" alt=""/>\r\n        </div>\r\n        \r\n        <div class="grid-5 columns formIntro">\r\n        	<h2>Start Beating Your Competition</h2>\r\n            <p>Claim your free, exclusive e-book written by our Partners at the Entrepreneurs Circle, The 7 Golden Rules of Profitable Restaurant Marketing, worth 9.99, and be the first to hear about our launch news and how you can join our growing Club </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n            \r\n            \r\n<div class="grid-4 columns guideForm">\r\n            \r\n                        <form accept-charset="UTF-8" action="https://vn172.infusionsoft.com/app/form/process/a009de1a3568bc0f35eacacce1d68480" class="infusion-form" method="POST">\r\n    <input name="inf_form_xid" type="hidden" value="a009de1a3568bc0f35eacacce1d68480" />\r\n    <input name="inf_form_name" type="hidden" value="FREE ebook" />\r\n    <input name="infusionsoft_version" type="hidden" value="1.29.10.21" />\r\n\r\n        <input class="watermark" id="inf_field_FirstName" name="inf_field_FirstName" type="text" placeholder="Name *" />\r\n\r\n        <input class="watermark" id="inf_field_Email" name="inf_field_Email" type="text" placeholder="Email *"/>\r\n\r\n    <input type="submit" value="Get your FREE e-book now" class="formSubmitButton" />    \r\n\r\n</form>\r\n            \r\n</div>\r\n'),
(540, '<img src="/index.php/download_file/view_inline/41/" alt="headerimage.jpg" width="2000" height="782" />\r\n\r\n<div class="row homeIntro">\r\n\r\n<div class="IntroTextHolder">\r\n\r\n<div class="columns grid-12">\r\n\r\n<h2 class="video">Wake up!...</h2>\r\n<p class="videoIntro">it''s time to join the new ''Go to'' website and Club for independent hospitality business owners.</p>\r\n\r\n<a href="#" class="video" data-reveal-id="VideoModal" data-reveal>Find Out More</a>\r\n\r\n<div class="VideoHide">Video to go here</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="grid-12 columns videoResponsive">\r\n<h2>It''s time...</h2>\r\n<p>for a new information and advice service for independent hospitality business owners.</p>\r\n<iframe width="853" height="480" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/vVUqpIRCLBs" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n'),
(541, '<h1>We Don''t Just Teach About Hospitality Entrepreneurship...</h1>\r\n<div class="under-big-title"><br />\r\n<p>We approach hospitality from a unique perspective. We all know that the challenges and demands of owning and running a restaurant, pub, bar, caf or hotel can be extreme, so extreme that the business usually ends up controlling us, preventing us from realising our goals and ambitions. So, since about 2001 we''ve been travelling the ''new'' world of hospitality, learning it, practising it and teaching it like no one else.</p>\r\n<p>The result is <strong>Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE)</strong> a new ''Go to'' information and advice website, a members'' ''Club'' and above all a ''get down and dirty'' practical service for smart hospitality business owners. No bland corporate crap here created to fill up a company webpage. Instead, <em>valuable</em> information, success secrets and exclusive access to services and systems that we consider to be the best way to grow a solid business.</p>\r\nOur mission will never change. We ensure that you get: <img src="http://hospitalityentrepreneur.com/member/images/about-he-image.png" alt="" align="right" /></div>\r\n<div class="under-big-title">\r\n<ul class="list-better">\r\n<li>Better <strong>profits</strong></li>\r\n<li>Better <strong>knowledge</strong></li>\r\n<li>Better <strong>peace of mind</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<h3>How do we do this?</h3>\r\n<p>Founder Peter Austen has been in the business of performance coaching for hundreds of hospitality businesses since 1993, before anyone (like the incredibly successful 2012 GB Olympic team) used that term. We hate to boast, but today we are a collaboration of leading industry professionals and companies, with thousands of happy clients and unrivalled expertise in building and running successful hospitality businesses.</p>\r\n<br />Every month we will release the best and latest industry advice (see Resources) to our members. This will be available for your use as and when you want it, 24/7, ready for you and your staff to implement straight away in your business. <br /><br />In addition to the best business advice, our members also enjoy privileged access to our Partner business services. <br /><br /><strong><em>Do you want to expand your business but dont know how?</em> </strong><br /><br /><strong><em>Would you like to radically increase your businesss profits whilst decreasing its reliance on YOU?</em> </strong><br /><br /><strong><em>Does your business control you, rather than the other way around?</em></strong> <br /><br />If the answer to any of these questions is yes, then you are a hospitality entrepreneur so join the Club today.</div>\r\n<h5></h5>'),
(542, '<h3>Articles, blogs, checklists and numerous trade secrets</h3>\r\n<p><img src="http://hospitalityentrepreneur.com/member/images/about-partners/partners-pics.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>from left to right: <strong>Andrew Pring, Carol Emmas, Peter Austen, Ali Carter and Nigel Botterill</strong></p>\r\n<p>A sprinkling of the hottest advice and help is provided by our assortment of writers and business experts.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Andrew Pring</strong>, our Business Editor has plenty to say on the business issues that are constantly changing the hospitality sector. With experience as editor at the Licensee &amp; Morning Advertiser and BII Business, he knows a fair bit about the pub industry especially. Also, <strong>Carol Emmas </strong>joins us from a recent stint as taste editor at Harpers Wine &amp; Spirit trade review when shes not writing for numerous hospitality publications.</p>\r\n<p>Insight and inspiration is provided by one of the countrys best known serial entrepreneurs, <strong>Nigel Botterill</strong>. He knows a fair bit about starting, expanding and selling multi-million pound businesses, having done that himself from scratch eight (at the last count!) times in the last ten years.</p>\r\n<p>Practical operational advice, including checklists, templates and behind the scenes insights is also provided by <strong>Peter Austen</strong> and <strong>Ali Carter</strong>, who have all the war stories and overview necessary after owning and running a variety of super-successful restaurants, hotels, pubs and bars themselves.</p>'),
(543, '<div class="member-benefit">\r\n<h3>Join Today</h3>\r\n<p>Join today using your exclusive 25% OFF VIP Launch Offer available to those who complete our <a href="http://hospitalityentrepreneur.com/survey.html">2 minute survey</a></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Attract and KEEP more customers</li>\r\n<li>Increase your bottom line profits</li>\r\n<li>Access exclusive member business resources 24/7</li>\r\n<li>Access easy-to-implement business growth secrets</li>\r\n<li>Benefit from the latest marketing, training and legal support</li>\r\n<li>Start implementing and benefitting, or your money back</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Subscribe for as little as 10 (plus VAT) per month or pay an annual subscription in one go for 120 (plus VAT) and enjoy 3 months extra for FREE</p>\r\n</div>'),
(544, '<h3>Member benefits</h3>\r\n<p><span>The most cost-effective way to take advantage of all that Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE) has to offer is to become a member of the HE club. </span></p>\r\n<p><span>Not only do you get access to every resource we produce, now and in the future, you benefit from a range of exclusive services that you simply cant get at a better price anywhere else. </span></p>'),
(545, '<div class="testBlock">\r\n<div class="testBlockInner">\r\n<p>Right now, 2014, has to be the best time to be an entrepreneur, especially if you are in the incredibly competitive industry that is hospitality. For both the Entrepreneur''s Circle and HE, we''ve gone out and already travelled the globe, scrutinising and learning from success in its many forms, met and worked with the most successful and applied it to our own businesses and those that we have the pleasure of working with. Peter Austen has been stalking me and pinning me down for over 15 months now and the result is one of my first ever strategic partnerships I''ve ever had the pleasure of working in. The fact is, if something is working well for someone else, there''s a very good chance that it''s going to work for you too, in YOUR business. Any serious entrepreneurs in hospitality would be bonkers not to join us!</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="testbottom"></div>\r\n<img src="http://www.hospitalityentrepreneur.com.gridhosted.co.uk/files/6913/9454/8783/test-image.png" alt="" />\r\n<h5>Nigel Botterill<span>Founder of Entrepreneurs Circle</span></h5>\r\n</div>'),
