(553, '<p><img src="{CCM:FID_71}" alt="Peter_pic2.jpg" width="94" height="111" /></p>\r\n<h3 class="MsoNormal"><strong>So, Who the Heck is Peter Austen?</strong></h3>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">HE was founded in July 2013 by Peter Austen. Peter is MD of the hospitality operations consultants Innventive, having spent the last 20 years immersed in hospitality business<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"> </span>coaching and operating pubs, restaurants, bars and hotels himself.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Peter is in a long line of successful entrepreneurs (and famous authors!), going back as far as ancestry and geneaology allow. More recently (?!), he is the third generation who have been entrepreneurs directly involved with hospitality. His grandparents established and operated one of the finest hotels in Britain, The Greenway <em>(pictured below)</em> in Gloucestershire for over 20 years from 1947, long before he himself started washing dishes, cleaning toilets, bottling up and serving customers at the age of 14.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><img src="{CCM:FID_70}" alt="greenway-hotel.jpg" width="304" height="204" /></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">He joined his father as a director in Austens, the first national firm of licensed trade accountants, consultants and stocktakers in 1994 before it was sold in 2000. Since then he has put into practice what he learned through family and clients at Austens, re-opening and operating a restaurant, two pubs, a hotel and a wine bar, all of which are still thriving today.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Peters move back to hospitality coaching since 2012 and to an online business model for coaching and mentoring comes from a conviction that success secrets are there to be shared and the very best way of doing that is through collaborating with those he respects most, creating an online information and advice website and a Club for those who really want to adapt, implement and thrive. The result of that move is Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE)  an innovative website and members Club that provides the advice and solutions that empower people to successfully grow their businesses through better marketing and operating.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Over the years, we''ve been fortunate that people say a lot of nice things about Peter, his businesses and, more recently, Hospitality Entrepreneur:</p>'),
