(571, '<h1>We Don''t Just Teach Hospitality Entrepreneurship...</h1>\r\n<div class="under-big-title"><br />\r\n<p>We approach hospitality from a unique perspective. We all know that the challenges and demands of owning and running a restaurant, pub, bar, caf or hotel can be extreme, so extreme that the business usually ends up controlling us, preventing us from realising our goals and ambitions. So, since about 2001 we''ve been travelling the ''new'' world of hospitality, learning it, practising it and teaching it like no one else.</p>\r\n<p>The result is <strong>Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE)</strong> a new ''Go to'' information and advice website, a members'' ''Club'' and above all a ''get down and dirty'' practical service for smart hospitality business owners. No bland corporate crap here created to fill up a company webpage. Instead, <em>valuable</em> information, success secrets and exclusive access to services and systems that we consider to be the best way to grow a solid business.</p>\r\nOur mission will never change. We ensure that you get: <img src="http://hospitalityentrepreneur.com/member/images/about-he-image.png" alt="" align="right" /></div>\r\n<div class="under-big-title">\r\n<ul class="list-better">\r\n<li>Better <strong>profits</strong></li>\r\n<li>Better <strong>knowledge</strong></li>\r\n<li>Better <strong>peace of mind</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<h3>How do we do this?</h3>\r\n<p>Founder Peter Austen has been in the business of performance coaching for hundreds of hospitality businesses since 1993, before anyone (like the incredibly successful 2012 GB Olympic team) used that term. We hate to boast, but today we are a collaboration of leading industry professionals and companies, with thousands of happy clients and unrivalled expertise in building and running successful hospitality businesses.</p>\r\n<br />Every month we will release the best and latest industry advice (see Resources) to our members. This will be available for your use as and when you want it, 24/7, ready for you and your staff to implement straight away in your business. <br /><br />In addition to the best business advice, our members also enjoy privileged access to our Partner business services. <br /><br /><strong><em>Do you want to expand your business but dont know how?</em> </strong><br /><br /><strong><em>Would you like to radically increase your businesss profits whilst decreasing its reliance on YOU?</em> </strong><br /><br /><strong><em>Does your business control you, rather than the other way around?</em></strong> <br /><br />If the answer to any of these questions is yes, then you are a hospitality entrepreneur so join our Club today.</div>\r\n<h5></h5>'),
(572, '<h3>Our Guarantees To You</h3>\r\n<p>We can guarantee that you''ll find the information, resources and advice incredibly inspirational, practical and easy to implement. No useless theory or rhetoric, just pratical tried and tested solutions or cutting edge ideas.</p>\r\n<p>For your <strong>FREE TRIAL</strong> Starter membership, if you don''t want to start paying just 10 a month after 30 days and don''t feel that ongoing membership will benefit your business, the fine, just tell us before the end of your 30 day <strong>FREE TRIAL</strong> and we''ll cancel your ongoing subscription. No questions asked, we won''t charge you a penny.</p>\r\n<p>For more serious entrepreneurs, we recognise your investment, time and involvement, so the guarantees are even stronger. If for some reason the HE website or our Partner businesses do not live up to our promises or <strong>Code of Conduct</strong>, then contact us within 30 days telling us where we went wrong and we will actually refund your first month''s subscription to that level of membership.</p>\r\n<p></p>'),
(573, '<div class="member-benefit">\r\n<h3>Join Today</h3>\r\n<p>Join today using your exclusive <strong>3 MONTHS EXTRA FOR FREE</strong> VIP Launch Offer available to those who complete our <a href="http://hospitalityentrepreneur.com/survey.html">2 minute survey</a> and take out annual subscription, or just dip your toe in with our FREE TRIAL Starter membership</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Attract and KEEP more customers</li>\r\n<li>Increase your bottom line profits</li>\r\n<li>Access exclusive member business resources 24/7</li>\r\n<li>Access easy-to-implement business growth secrets</li>\r\n<li>Benefit from the latest purchasing, marketing, training, food costing and legal support</li>\r\n<li>Start implementing and benefitting, or your money back</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Subscribe for as little as 10 (plus VAT) per month or pay an annual subscription in one go for 120 (plus VAT) and enjoy 3 months extra for FREE</p>\r\n</div>'),
(576, '<h1>Our Partners</h1>\r\n<p><span>A collaboration of tried and tested industry suppliers and professionals provide you with the best possible service. They have</span> <span><span>proven, unrivalled experience and expertise in supplying and running literally thousands of profitable hospitality businesses. Our Partners are driven by a shared vision for providing increased profitability, knowledge and peace of mind for our members. <br /><br />We are also in discussion with additional market leading companies and content providers, with the aim of making Hospitality Entrepreneur unquestionably beneficial to our membership. </span></span></p>'),
