(805, '<h1>Marvellous PR</h1>\r\n<h4>Marvellous PR from Lucy Matthews  The UK Entrepreneurs PR Expert</h4>\r\n<p><span>In a 30+ year career as a PR consultant, Lucy Matthews has worked with a huge range of clients in B2B and B2C markets, around the world, from industrial floor cleaning manufacturers, to football clubs; property developers to therapists; Pepsi to pasta ready meals; photographers to authors; big businesses to entrepreneurs and small start-ups; helping them to build their profile and get free editorial.</span></p>'),
