(807, '<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">FREE TRIAL PAGE / REGISTRATION PAGE:</span></strong></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><em>&lt;INSERT Bottys Rules image&gt;</em></p>\r\n<p>In addition to receiving your FREE copy of the Sunday Times bestseller Bottys Rules (RRP 12.99) in the post*, when you claim your free Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE) 30 day trial, youll get a taste of our exclusive members benefits:</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>KNOWLEDGE: </strong><strong></strong><strong></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>24/7 access to at least 70% of downloadable HE website member advice and business resources</li>\r\n<li>Members Only business building blogs from our editors and Partners</li>\r\n<li><strong>PEACE OF MIND:</strong><strong></strong><strong></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Your own Business Health Check questionnaire</li>\r\n<li>Templates, checklists and systems to start using in your business today</li>\r\n<li><strong>PROFIT: </strong><strong></strong><strong></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Exclusive access and unique deals with our Partner business services</li>\r\n<li>Ready-to-use profit boosting strategies</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>and instant access to a treasure chest of proven hospitality marketing and operations nuggets including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Marketing :</strong> the latest hospitality marketing tips, online and offline trends and best practices</li>\r\n<li><strong>Exclusive HE videos :</strong> hospitality how-to, in weekly released videos from industry top performers</li>\r\n<li><strong>Entrepreneur skills :</strong> everything you need to start controlling and growing your business TODAY</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>* Sorry, Bottys Rules is only available to UK business address subscribers at present</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>SUBSCRIBE TODAY OR MODIFY YOUR HE MEMBERSHIP BELOW:</p>\r\n<p align="center"><strong>Register Here</strong></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><em>&lt; screen 1&gt;</em></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>First Name:</p>\r\n<p>Last Name:</p>\r\n<p>Email Address:</p>\r\n<p>Password:</p>\r\n<p>Re-enter Password:</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n</div>'),
(808, '<div>\r\n<p><strong>PAYMENT DETAILS:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Note: You will be asked to provide payment details before your 30 day FREE trial starts. Once you register, youll have continuous access to the HE members website via the username and password you choose. Well also send you brief announcements when new content is posted. As always, we respect your privacy, and you can unsubscribe at any time. Whats more, if you are not entirely happy during your first 30 days, you can unsubscribe and you will not be charged a penny, dime, yen or whatever your chosen currency.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>Youll also receive HUMAN induction and welcome calls from both Peter Austen (HE founder) and our partners at Nigel Botterills Entrepreneurs Circle during your 300 day trial.</p>\r\n<p>In other words, by signing up right now, and putting into practice what youll learn, youll soon join the ranks of some of the smartest hospitality pros on the planet.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>'),
(812, '<h1>YOUR FREE TRIAL</h1>\r\n<p>In addition to receiving your FREE copy of the Sunday Times bestseller Bottys Rules (RRP 12.99) in the post*, when you claim your free Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE) 30 day trial, youll get a taste of our exclusive members benefits:</p>\r\n<p><strong>KNOWLEDGE:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>24/7 access to at least 70% of downloadable HE website member advice and business resources</li>\r\n<li>Members Only business building blogs from our editors and Partners</li>\r\n<li><strong><br /></strong></li>\r\n<li><strong><br /></strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>PEACE OF MIND:</strong></li>\r\n<li>Your own Business Health Check questionnaire</li>\r\n<li>Templates, checklists and systems to start using in your business today</li>\r\n<li><strong><br /></strong></li>\r\n<li><strong><br /></strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>PROFIT:</strong></li>\r\n<li>Exclusive access and unique deals with our Partner business services</li>\r\n<li>Ready-to-use profit boosting strategies</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>and instant access to a treasure chest of proven hospitality marketing and operations nuggets including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Marketing :</strong> the latest hospitality marketing tips, online and offline trends and best practices</li>\r\n<li><strong>Exclusive HE videos :</strong> hospitality how-to, in weekly released videos from industry top performers</li>\r\n<li><strong>Entrepreneur skills :</strong> everything you need to start controlling and growing your business TODAY</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p align="center"><strong>Register Now (It''s Free)</strong></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n</div>'),
(813, '<h1 style="text-align: center;">YOUR FREE TRIAL</h1>\r\n<div class="grid-10 columns nopadLeft">\r\n<h4>In addition to receiving your FREE copy of the Sunday Times bestseller Bottys Rules (RRP 12.99) in the post*, when you claim your free Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE) 30 day trial, youll get a taste of our exclusive members benefits:</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grid-2 columns nopadRight"><img src="{CCM:FID_143}" alt="bottyrules.jpg" width="180" height="288" /></div>\r\n<h3><strong>KNOWLEDGE:</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>24/7 access to at least 70% of downloadable HE website member advice and business resources</li>\r\n<li>Members Only business building blogs from our editors and Partners</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>PEACE OF MIND:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Your own Business Health Check questionnaire</li>\r\n<li>Templates, checklists and systems to start using in your business today</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>PROFIT:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Exclusive access and unique deals with our Partner business services</li>\r\n<li>Ready-to-use profit boosting strategies</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>and instant access to a treasure chest of proven hospitality marketing and operations nuggets including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Marketing :</strong> the latest hospitality marketing tips, online and offline trends and best practices</li>\r\n<li><strong>Exclusive HE videos :</strong> hospitality how-to, in weekly released videos from industry top performers</li>\r\n<li><strong>Entrepreneur skills :</strong> everything you need to start controlling and growing your business TODAY</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align="center"><strong>Register Now (It''s Free)</strong></p>\r\n<div></div>'),
(815, '<h1>Entrepreneurs Circle</h1>\r\n<p><iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/5qs4KO0Hsnw" frameborder="0" width="640" height="480"></iframe></p>\r\n<h2>The UKs Largest Membership Organisation Dedicated to Helping Business Grow</h2>\r\n<h4>Key services and benefits to members</h4>\r\n<p><span>In the last 8 years Nigel Botterill has built 8 separate 1m businesses from scratch, so he knows a thing or two about business growth. Nigels Entrepreneurs Circle is the UKs largest membership organisation dedicated to helping business grow. With a national network of Business Growth Advisors (BGAs) and 130 local meetings each month across the UK, thousands of entrepreneurs have been helped by discovering new ideas and then making them work in their own businesses. Now we have joined forces to launch a business advice and ''done for you'' marketing service tailored for hospitality.</span><br /><br /><span>All Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE) ''Starter'' members gain marketing and business growth advice and tips from Nigel and his advisors from Day 1, posted regularly on our website and blogs. Whilst Starter subscription to HE does not include membership of the Entrepreneurs Circle, you can qualify for preferential and exclusive joining fees, especially for the new Club Plus membership level which we are launching in March.</span></p>\r\n<h4>How this can help you</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Business strategy</li>\r\n<li>How to maximise you Marketing</li>\r\n<li>much much more</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>See our Membership page to find out how you can join Nigels Entrepreneurs Circle and have automatic exclusive access to his Club Plus Membership (usually 299 per month) and an additional marketing and business growth package that has been tailored to our industry.</p>'),
(816, '<h1>Entrepreneurs Circle</h1>\r\n<p><iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/5qs4KO0Hsnw?&amp;autoplay=1&amp;rel=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;autohide=1" frameborder="0" width="640" height="480"></iframe></p>\r\n<h2>The UKs Largest Membership Organisation Dedicated to Helping Business Grow</h2>\r\n<h4>Key services and benefits to members</h4>\r\n<p><span>In the last 8 years Nigel Botterill has built 8 separate 1m businesses from scratch, so he knows a thing or two about business growth. Nigels Entrepreneurs Circle is the UKs largest membership organisation dedicated to helping business grow. With a national network of Business Growth Advisors (BGAs) and 130 local meetings each month across the UK, thousands of entrepreneurs have been helped by discovering new ideas and then making them work in their own businesses. Now we have joined forces to launch a business advice and ''done for you'' marketing service tailored for hospitality.</span><br /><br /><span>All Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE) ''Starter'' members gain marketing and business growth advice and tips from Nigel and his advisors from Day 1, posted regularly on our website and blogs. Whilst Starter subscription to HE does not include membership of the Entrepreneurs Circle, you can qualify for preferential and exclusive joining fees, especially for the new Club Plus membership level which we are launching in March.</span></p>\r\n<h4>How this can help you</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Business strategy</li>\r\n<li>How to maximise you Marketing</li>\r\n<li>much much more</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>See our Membership page to find out how you can join Nigels Entrepreneurs Circle and have automatic exclusive access to his Club Plus Membership (usually 299 per month) and an additional marketing and business growth package that has been tailored to our industry.</p>'),
