(917, '<h3 class="home centered"><span>Solutions</span> for smarter hospitality</h3>\r\n<p class="centered textPad">It''s like having your own personal industry expert with you full time, but without having to pay the expensive day rate. As a ground breaking new collaboration of proven industry experts and companies, we can ensure you get better profits, better knowledge and better peace of mind.</p>\r\n<h3 class="centered textPad">Here''s what we''ve got for you:</h3>\r\n<div class="grid-6 column">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>24/7 advice and success ''secrets'' from entrepreneurs and hospitality business owners, like you, to provide expert guidance to hospitality business owners, like you!</li>\r\n<li>inspiration, exclusive insights, practical help, 1:1 mentoring</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grid-6 column">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>a real chance to control and grow your business before it controls you</li>\r\n<li>years of combined knowledge, experience and systems gift-wrapped for you</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>'),
