(998, '<!--<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/XnAoBOpfds4?rel=0?&autoplay=1&rel=0&fs=0&showinfo=0&modestbranding=1&autohide=1" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>-->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/2Bdm89UPZKA?&autoplay=1&rel=0&fs=0&showinfo=0&modestbranding=1&autohide=1" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>'),
(999, '<h2>It''s time to join the new Club</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Take <strong> YOUR FREE 30 DAY</strong> trial of the No1 resource in the UK today for independent hospitality business owners looking to take their businesses to the next level.</p>\r\n'),
(1000, '<h1>We Don''t Just Waffle About Hospitality Entrepreneurship...</h1>\r\n<p><iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/XnAoBOpfds4?rel=0?rel=0&amp;fs=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;autohide=1" frameborder="0" width="560" height="315"></iframe></p>\r\n<div class="under-big-title">\r\n<p>We approach hospitality from a unique perspective. We all know that the challenges and demands of owning and running a restaurant, pub, bar, caf or hotel can be extreme, so extreme that the business usually ends up controlling you, preventing you from realising your goals and ambitions. So, since the 1990''s and even more since 2001 we''ve been travelling the ''new'' world of hospitality, learning it, practising it and teaching it like no one else.</p>\r\n<p>The result is <strong>Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE)</strong> a new ''Go to'' information and advice website, a members'' ''Club'' and above all a ''get down and dirty'' practical service for smart hospitality business owners. No bland corporate waffle here, created just to fill up a company webpage. Instead, <em>valuable</em> information, success secrets from those at the top of the hospitality tree and exclusive access to services and systems that we consider to be the best way to grow a solid business.</p>\r\n<strong>Our mission will never change. We ensure that you get:</strong></div>\r\n<div class="under-big-title">\r\n<ul class="list-better">\r\n<li>Better <strong>profits</strong></li>\r\n<li>Better <strong>knowledge</strong></li>\r\n<li>Better <strong>peace of mind</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>How do we do this?</h4>\r\n<p>Founder Peter Austen has been in the business of performance coaching for hundreds of hospitality businesses since 1993, before anyone used that term. We hate to boast, but today we are a collaboration of leading industry professionals and companies, with thousands of happy clients and unrivalled expertise in building and running successful hospitality businesses.</p>\r\n<br />Every month we will release the best and latest industry advice (see Resources) to our members. This will be available for your use as and when you want it, 24/7, ready for you and your staff to implement straight away in your business. <br /><br />In addition to the best business advice, our members also enjoy privileged access to our Partner business services. <br /><br />\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Do you want to expand your business but dont know how? </strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Would you like to radically increase your businesss profits whilst decreasing its reliance on YOU?</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Does your business control you, rather than the other way around?</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />If the answer to any of these questions is ''YES'', then you are a hospitality entrepreneur, so join our Club today.</div>\r\n<h5></h5>'),
(1001, '<div class="sideForm">\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n<h2>Start beating your competition</h2>\r\n<img src="/files/6513/9904/0881/bottyrules.jpg" alt="Bottys Rules"/>\r\n<p>Claim a FREE copy of ''Botty''s Rules'', the Sunday Times Bestseller, written by Nigel Botterill, founder of the Entrepreneurs Circle.</p>\r\n\r\n    \r\n<form accept-charset="UTF-8" action="https://vn172.infusionsoft.com/app/form/process/a009de1a3568bc0f35eacacce1d68480" class="infusion-form" method="POST">\r\n    <input name="inf_form_xid" type="hidden" value="a009de1a3568bc0f35eacacce1d68480" />\r\n    <input name="inf_form_name" type="hidden" value="FREE ebook" />\r\n    <input name="infusionsoft_version" type="hidden" value="1.29.10.21" />\r\n\r\n        <input class="watermark" id="inf_field_FirstName" name="inf_field_FirstName" type="text" placeholder="Name *" />\r\n\r\n        <input class="watermark" id="inf_field_Email" name="inf_field_Email" type="text" placeholder="Email *"/>\r\n\r\n    <input type="submit" value="Get your FREE book now" class="formSubmitButton" />    \r\n\r\n</form>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n            '),
(1002, '<div class="guaranteeBox"><img style="float: right; margin-right: 20px;" src="{CCM:FID_163}" alt="Guarantee.jpg" width="202" height="142" /><br />\r\n<h3>Our Guarantees To You</h3>\r\n<p>We can guarantee that you''ll find the information, resources and advice incredibly inspirational, practical and easy to implement. No waffle, useless theory or rhetoric, just pratical tried and tested solutions or cutting edge ideas.</p>\r\n<p>For your <strong>FREE TRIAL</strong> Starter membership, if you don''t want to start paying just 10 a month after 30 days and don''t feel that ongoing membership will benefit your business, then fine, just tell us before the end of your 30 day <strong>FREE TRIAL</strong> and we''ll cancel your ongoing subscription. No questions asked, we won''t charge you a penny.</p>\r\n<p>For more serious entrepreneurs, we recognise your investment, time and involvement, so the guarantees are even stronger. If for some reason the HE website or our Partner businesses do not live up to our promises or <strong>Code of Conduct</strong>, then contact us within 30 days telling us where we went wrong and we will actually refund your first month''s subscription to that level of membership.</p>\r\n</div>'),
(1003, '<div class="membersSignUpSide">\r\n<h4 id="plussideintro">Subscribe to Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE)</h4>\r\n<p>Premium content that helps you make the right decisions, take the right actions, and focus on what really matters and take your business to the next level.</p>\r\n<a class="membButtSide sideButt" href="/membership/#membership">Click here to view our membership options</a></div>'),
