(1009, '<h3 class="home centered greenHeader" style="padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;"><strong>Simple, smart and sustainable business growth</strong> ''secrets''</h3>\r\n<h3><strong>Do you want to expand your business, but don''t know how?</strong></h3>\r\n<h3><br /><strong>Does your business control you, rather than the other way round?</strong></h3>\r\n<h3><br /><strong>Do you want to know which changes could double your annual profits?</strong></h3>\r\n<h3><br /><strong>Would you have more control if you could delegate more effectively?</strong></h3>\r\n<p><strong><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p class="centered textPad" style="text-align: left;">Hospitality Entrepreneur (''HE'') provides answers to all the above. It''s like having your own personal industry expert with you full time, but without having to pay the expensive day rate. The result of a ground breaking new collaboration of proven industry experts and companies, we really can ensure you get better profits, better knowledge and better peace of mind.</p>\r\n<h3 class="centered textPad">Here''s what we''ve got for you:</h3>\r\n<div class="grid-6 column">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>24/7 advice, guidance, systems and success ''secrets'' at your fingertips, from the most successful entrepreneurs and hospitality business owners, just like you</li>\r\n<li>inspiration, exclusive insights, practical help, templates and resources</li>\r\n<li>1:1 mentoring from real people, not just a website or out of date tips on a PDF</li>\r\n<li>a ''done for you'' marketing support package</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grid-6 column">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>a real chance to control and grow your business before it controls you</li>\r\n<li>years of combined knowledge, experience and systems gift-wrapped for you</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>'),
(1011, '<h3 class="home" style="text-align: left;"><span>Who''s involved?</span> A total collaboration for you</h3>\r\n<p class="centered textPad" style="text-align: left;">Leading industry suppliers and professionals bring proven, unrivalled experience and expertise in supplying and actually running profitable hospitality businesses. Our Partners are driven by a shared vision for providing increased profitability, knowledge and peace of mind for our members.</p>\r\n<p class="centered textPad" style="text-align: left;"><span style="line-height: 115%;">The HE advisors and partners have already had the sleepless nights worrying about staff, premises and bills that need paying yesterday, so why not let them share their advice with you (theyve had their fair share of celebrations, financial successes</span> and Champagne popping also)?</p>');
