(1016, '<h3 class="home centered greenHeader" style="padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;"><strong>Simple, smart and sustainable business growth</strong> ''secrets''</h3>\r\n<h3><strong>Do you want to expand your business, but don''t know how?</strong></h3>\r\n<h3><br /><strong>Does your business control you, rather than the other way round?</strong></h3>\r\n<h3><br /><strong>Do you want to know which changes could double your annual profits?</strong></h3>\r\n<h3><br /><strong>Could you control your business by delegating and outsourcing more effectively?</strong></h3>\r\n<p><strong><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p class="centered textPad" style="text-align: left;">Well, GOOD NEWS!, because Hospitality Entrepreneur (''HE'') provides answers to all the above. We''re a bit like having your own personal industry expert with you full time, but a lot less boring and without having to pay the expensive day rate. The result of a ground breaking new collaboration of proven industry experts and companies, we really can (and DO!) ensure you get better profits, better knowledge and better peace of mind.</p>\r\n<h3 class="centered textPad">Here''s what we''ve got for you:</h3>\r\n<div class="grid-6 column">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>24/7 advice, guidance, systems and success ''secrets'' at your fingertips, from the most successful entrepreneurs and hospitality business owners, just like you</li>\r\n<li>inspiration, exclusive insights, practical help, templates and resources</li>\r\n<li>1:1 mentoring from real people, not just a website or out of date tips on a PDF</li>\r\n<li>a revolutionary ''done for you'' marketing support package</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grid-6 column">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>a real chance to control and grow your business before it controls you</li>\r\n<li>years of combined knowledge, experience and systems gift-wrapped for you</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>'),
(1017, '<h3 class="home" style="text-align: left;"><span>Who''s involved?</span></h3>\r\n<p class="centered textPad" style="text-align: left;">We can bring you a unique collaboration, with unrivalled experience and expertise in supplying and actually running profitable hospitality businesses. Our contributors and Partners are driven by a shared vision for providing increased profitability, knowledge and peace of mind for our members.</p>\r\n<p class="centered textPad" style="text-align: left;"><span style="line-height: 115%;">Like you, we''ve also experienced the sleepless nights worrying about staff, premises and bills that need paying yesterday, so why not let us share our advice with you, especially as we''ve had our fair share of celebrations, financial successes</span> and Champagne popping also!</p>'),
(1018, '<h1>We Don''t Just Waffle About Hospitality Entrepreneurship...</h1>\r\n<p><iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/XnAoBOpfds4?rel=0?rel=0&amp;fs=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;autohide=1" frameborder="0" width="560" height="315"></iframe></p>\r\n<div class="under-big-title">\r\n<p>We approach hospitality from a unique perspective. We all know that the challenges and demands of owning and running a restaurant, pub, bar, caf or hotel can be extreme, so extreme that the business usually ends up controlling you, preventing you from realising your goals and ambitions. So, since the 1990''s and even more since 2001 we''ve been travelling the ''new'' world of hospitality, learning it, practising it and teaching it like no one else.</p>\r\n<p>The result is <strong>Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE)</strong> a new ''Go to'' information and advice website, a members'' ''Club'' and above all a ''get down and dirty'' practical service for smart hospitality business owners. No bland corporate waffle here, created just to fill up a company webpage. Instead, <em>valuable</em> information, success secrets from those at the top of the hospitality tree and exclusive access to services and systems that we consider to be the best way to grow a solid business.</p>\r\n<strong>Our mission will never change. We ensure that you get:</strong></div>\r\n<div class="under-big-title">\r\n<ul class="list-better">\r\n<li>Better <strong>profits</strong></li>\r\n<li>Better <strong>knowledge</strong></li>\r\n<li>Better <strong>peace of mind</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><strong><span style="color: #99cc00;">How do we do this?</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p>''HE'' founder Peter Austen has been in the business of performance coaching for hundreds of hospitality businesses since 1993, before anyone used that term. We hate to boast, but today we are a collaboration of leading industry professionals and companies, with thousands of happy clients and unrivalled expertise in building and running successful hospitality businesses.</p>\r\n<br />Every month we will release the best and latest industry advice (see Resources) to our members. This will be available for your use as and when you want it, 24/7, ready for you and your staff to implement straight away in your business. <br /><br />In addition to the best business advice, our members also enjoy privileged direct access to our Partner business services. <br /><br />\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Do you want to expand your business but dont quite know how? </strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Would you like to radically increase your businesss profits whilst decreasing its reliance on YOU?</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Does your business control you, rather than the other way around?</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />If you feel the answer to any of these questions is ''YES'', then you are almost certainly a hospitality entrepreneur, so take the FREE TRIAL and join our Club today!</div>\r\n<h5></h5>'),
(1019, '<h4>Videos, articles, blogs, checklists and numerous trade secrets</h4>\r\n<p><img src="http://hospitalityentrepreneur.com/member/images/about-partners/partners-pics.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>Clockwise from top left: <strong>Andrew Pring, Carol Emmas, Peter Austen, Nigel Botterill and Ali Carter<br /></strong></p>\r\n<p>A sprinkling of the hottest advice and help is provided by our assortment of writers and business experts.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Andrew Pring</strong>, our Business Editor has plenty to say on the business issues that are constantly changing the hospitality sector. With experience as editor at the Licensee &amp; Morning Advertiser and BII Business, he knows a fair bit about the pub industry especially. Also, <strong>Carol Emmas </strong>joins us from a recent stint as taste editor at Harpers Wine &amp; Spirit trade review when shes not writing for numerous hospitality publications.</p>\r\n<p>Insight and inspiration is provided by one of the countrys best known serial entrepreneurs, <strong>Nigel Botterill</strong>. He knows a fair bit about starting, expanding and selling multi-million pound businesses, having done that himself from scratch eight (at the last count!) times in the last ten years.</p>\r\n<p>Practical operational advice, including checklists, templates and behind the scenes insights, is also provided by <strong>Peter Austen</strong> and <strong>Ali Carter</strong>, who have all the war stories and overview necessary after owning and running a variety of super-successful restaurants, hotels, pubs and bars themselves.</p>'),
(1020, '<h3 class="MsoNormal"><a title="So, who is Peter Austen?" href="{CCM:CID_322}"><strong>So, who is Peter Austen?</strong></a></h3>\r\n<p><img style="float: left; margin-right: 20px;" src="{CCM:FID_71}" alt="Peter_pic2.jpg" width="94" height="111" /></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE) was founded in July 2013 by Peter Austen. Peter is MD of the hospitality operations consultants Innventive, having spent the last 20 years immersed in hospitality business<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"> </span>coaching and operating pubs, restaurants, bars and hotels himself.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><a title="So, who is Peter Austen?" href="{CCM:CID_322}"><strong>Find out more about Peter</strong></a></p>\r\n<p></p>'),
(1021, '<div class="member-benefit">\r\n<h2 class="home greenHeader"><span style="color: #99cc00;"><strong>Join Today</strong></span></h2>\r\n<p>Join today, either by taking advantage of our Starter membership 30 day <strong>FREE</strong> trial or, if you''ve been lucky enough to have been contacted by one of our Partner businesses, using your exclusive VIP Launch Offer.</p>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #99cc00;"><strong>Starter membership - 30 day FREE trial</strong></span></h3>\r\n<p>Dip your toe in, receive a FREE copy of the 245 page ''Botty''s Rules'', enjoy access to 70% of the HE website and resources, as well as privileged access to our Partner business services<strong><br /></strong></p>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #99cc00;"><strong>Exclusive VIP Launch Offer</strong></span></h3>\r\n<p><strong></strong>Our VIP Launch Offer, including 3 months extra subscription for <strong>FREE, </strong>is available to friends of our Partner businesses and those of you who complete our <a href="http://hospitalityentrepreneur.com/survey.html">2 minute survey</a> when you take out annual subscription</p>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #99cc00;"><strong>Either way, join the HE Club now and start to:</strong></span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Attract and KEEP more customers</li>\r\n<li>Increase your bottom line profits</li>\r\n<li>Access exclusive member business resources 24/7</li>\r\n<li>Access easy-to-implement business growth secrets</li>\r\n<li>Benefit from the latest purchasing, marketing, training, food costing and operations support</li>\r\n<li>Start implementing and benefitting, or your money back</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #99cc00;"><strong>It''s all here for as little as 10 (plus VAT) per month</strong></span></h3>\r\n</div>'),
(1022, '<div class="sideForm">\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2>Enjoy Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE) FREE for 30 days</h2>\r\n<img src="/files/3213/9600/3699/Free-30-day-trial.png" alt="Hospitality Entrepreneur FREE Trial"/>\r\n\r\n<p>Gain access to at least 70% of the HE website, test drive our Member benefits and resources, be among the first to hear about our launch news and benefit from being a part of our growing Club </p>\r\n\r\n<form accept-charset="UTF-8" action="https://vn172.infusionsoft.com/app/form/process/ee5d812dae477bcbf1a40ca93633f17c" class="infusion-form" method="POST">\r\n    <input name="inf_form_xid" type="hidden" value="ee5d812dae477bcbf1a40ca93633f17c" />\r\n    <input name="inf_form_name" type="hidden" value="FREE Trial First Step" />\r\n    <input name="infusionsoft_version" type="hidden" value="1.29.11.21" />\r\n    \r\n     \r\n     <input type="text" id="inf_field_Email" name="inf_field_Email" value="Your Email Address" class="watermark" />\r\n<input type="submit" id="register" value="Get your FREE Trial NOW" disabled="disabled" class="regButt" />\r\n\r\n</form>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<script type="text/javascript" >\r\n(function() {\r\n    $(''form > input'').keyup(function() {\r\n\r\n        var empty = false;\r\n        $(''form > input'').each(function() {\r\n            if ($(this).val() == '''') {\r\n                empty = true;\r\n            }\r\n        });\r\n\r\n        if (empty) {\r\n            $(''#register'').attr(''disabled'', ''disabled'');\r\n        } else {\r\n            $(''#register'').removeAttr(''disabled'');\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n})()\r\n\r\n</script>'),
(1023, '<div class="membersSignUpSide">\r\n<h4 id="plussideintro">Subscribe to Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE)</h4>\r\n<p>Unique guidance and premium content that helps you make the right decisions, take the right actions, focus on what really matters and takes your business to the next level.</p>\r\n<a class="membButtSide sideButt" href="/membership#membershiptable">Click here to view our membership options</a></div>'),
(1024, '<p><img src="{CCM:FID_71}" alt="Peter_pic2.jpg" width="94" height="111" /></p>\r\n<h3 class="MsoNormal"><strong>So, who is Peter Austen?</strong></h3>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE) was founded at the end of 2013 by Peter Austen. Peter is MD of the hospitality operations consultants Innventive, having spent the last 20 years immersed in hospitality business<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"> </span>coaching and operating pubs, restaurants, bars and hotels himself.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Peter is in a long line of successful entrepreneurs (and famous authors!), going back almost as far as ancestry and geneaology allow. More recently (?!), he is the third generation who have been entrepreneurs directly involved with hospitality. His grandparents bought, established and operated one of the finest hotels in Britain, The Greenway <em>(pictured below)</em> in Gloucestershire for over 20 years from 1947, long before he himself started washing dishes, cleaning toilets, bottling up and serving customers at the age of 14.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><img src="{CCM:FID_164}" alt="Greenway-Exterior_2.jpg" width="331" height="162" /></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">He joined his father as a director in Austens, the first national firm of licensed trade accountants, consultants and stocktakers in 1994 before it was sold in 2000. Since then he has put into practice what he learned through family and clients at Austens, re-opening and operating a restaurant, two pubs, a hotel and a wine bar, all of which are still thriving today.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><img src="{CCM:FID_95}" alt="Sausage_staff_pic.jpg" width="347" height="460" /></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Peters move back to hospitality coaching since 2012 and to an online business model for coaching and mentoring comes from a conviction that success secrets are there to be shared and the very best way of doing that is through collaborating with those he respects most, creating an online information and advice website and a Club for those who really want to adapt, implement and thrive. The result of that move is Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE)  an innovative website and members Club that provides the advice and solutions that empower people to successfully grow their businesses through better marketing and operating.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Over the years, we''ve been fortunate that people say a lot of nice things about Peter, his businesses and, more recently, HE:</p>'),
