(1105, '<h1>Cater Cost</h1>\r\n<p>Knowing down to the last penny the cost of the food you make and sell on your menu can be tricky  especially if you make dishes from scratch and yet its a basic principle of retail to know your costs to ensure you make your margins!<br />CaterCost will add s to your bottom line food profit without time-consuming number-crunching <br /><br /><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Facts about independent food operators:</strong></p>\r\n<p><br />98% dont have an accurate dish specification<br />Only 2% know their cashcow dishes<br />Food waste for an avergage restaurant is valued at 17,000 a year!<br /><br />Thats why you need to take control <br /><br /><strong></strong></p>\r\n<h3><strong>Why CaterCost?</strong><br /><br /></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Uber user-friendly</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Dish costing as quick as a wink  or as quick as you can type</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Menu library  forget scraps of paper</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Profit alerts  flag underperforming dishes</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Easy-cost sub-recipes  normally pretty tricky but CaterCost turns sub-recipes into fully costed entities you can use in any quantity you like</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>One click price change</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Nutritional analysis  as it costs it calculates  Kcal, salt, fat, carb, protein per dish</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>NEW unique 14 allergen tracking and menu scanning App  the law changes 13th Dec  are you ready?</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><br /><br /><br /></p>'),
