(1148, '<h1 class="home centered greenHeader" style="padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;"><strong>Simple, smart and sustainable business growth ''secrets'', every month</strong></h1>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left; padding-left: 60px;"><span style="font-size: 1em;">Do you want to <strong>expand your business</strong>, but don''t know how?</span></h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left; padding-left: 60px;"><br />Does your <strong>business control you</strong>, rather than the other way round?</h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left; padding-left: 60px;"><br />Do you want to know which changes could <strong>double your annual profits</strong>?</h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left; padding-left: 60px;"><br />Could you control your business by <strong>delegating and outsourcing</strong> more effectively?</h3>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p class="centered textPad" style="text-align: left;">Well, GOOD NEWS!, because Hospitality Entrepreneur (''HE'') provides answers to all the above. We''re a bit like having your own personal industry expert with you full time, but a lot less boring and without having to pay the expensive day rate. The result of a ground breaking new collaboration of proven industry experts and companies, we really can (and DO!) ensure you get better profits, better knowledge and better peace of mind.</p>\r\n<h3 class="centered textPad">Here''s what we''ve got for you:</h3>\r\n<div class="grid-6 column">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>24/7 advice, guidance, systems and success ''secrets'' at your fingertips, from the most successful entrepreneurs and hospitality business owners, just like you</li>\r\n<li>inspiration, exclusive insights, practical help, templates and resources, released and updated every month</li>\r\n<li>a revolutionary ''done for you'' marketing support package</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grid-6 column">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>a real chance to control and grow your business before it controls you</li>\r\n<