(1171, '<h3 class="home" style="text-align: center;"><span>Who''s involved?</span></h3>\r\n<p class="centered textPad" style="text-align: left;">We can bring you a unique collaboration, with unrivalled experience and expertise in supplying and actually running profitable hospitality businesses. Our contributors and Partners are driven by a shared vision for providing increased profitability, knowledge and peace of mind for our members.</p>\r\n<p class="centered textPad" style="text-align: left;"><span style="line-height: 115%;">Like you, we''ve also experienced the sleepless nights worrying about staff, premises and bills that need paying yesterday. So why not let us share our advice with you, especially as we''ve had our fair share of celebrations, financial successes</span> and Champagne popping also!</p>'),
