(1179, '<h3>July members'' benefits:</h3>\r\n<ul class="whiteTick">\r\n<li>Exclusive video interviews with Alex Reilley, MD Lounges and Cosy Clubs</li>\r\n<li>NEW revolutionary<strong>Club Plus </strong>''done for you'' marketing package</li>\r\n<li>Lots of new resources ready to help you grow your business</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1180, '<h4>Videos, articles, blogs, checklists and numerous trade secrets</h4>\r\n<p><img src="{CCM:BASE_URL}/member/images/about-partners/partners-pics.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><strong><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p>A sprinkling of the hottest advice and help is provided by our assortment of writers and business experts.</p>\r\n<p>Insight and inspiration is provided by one of the countrys best known serial entrepreneurs, <strong>Nigel Botterill</strong>. He knows a fair bit about starting, expanding and selling multi-million pound businesses, having done that himself from scratch eight (at the last count!) times in the last ten years.</p>\r\n<p>Practical operational advice, including checklists, templates and behind the scenes insights, is also provided by <strong>Peter Austen</strong> and <strong>Ali Carter</strong>, who have all the war stories and overview necessary after owning and running a variety of super-successful restaurants, hotels, pubs and bars themselves.</p>'),
(1181, '<h3>August members'' benefits:</h3>\r\n<ul class="whiteTick">\r\n<li>NEW revolutionary <strong>Club Plus</strong> and<strong>Premier</strong>''done for you'' marketing package</li>\r\n<li>NEW exclusive member-only resources ready to help you grow your business</li>\r\n<li>NEW HE video Part 2 with Alex Reilley, MD Lounges and Cosy Clubs</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1182, '<h1>Entrepreneur''s Circle</h1>\r\n<p><iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/5qs4KO0Hsnw?&amp;autoplay=1&amp;rel=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;autohide=1" frameborder="0" width="640" height="480"></iframe></p>\r\n<h2>The UKs Largest Membership Organisation Dedicated to Helping Business Grow, with an <strong>unbeatable and exclusive new offer for August..</strong></h2>\r\n<h4>Key services and benefits to members</h4>\r\n<p><span>In the last 8 years Nigel Botterill has built 8 separate 1m businesses from scratch, so he knows a thing or two about business growth. Nigels Entrepreneurs Circle is the UKs largest membership organisation dedicated to helping business grow. With a national network of Business Growth Advisors (BGAs) and 130 local meetings each month across the UK, thousands of entrepreneurs have been helped by discovering new ideas and then making them work in their own businesses. Now we have joined forces to launch a business advice and a choice of <strong>TWO</strong> ''done for you'' marketing services tailored for hospitality.</span><br /><br /><span>All Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE) ''Starter'' members gain marketing and business growth advice and tips from Nigel and his advisors from Day 1, posted regularly on our website and blogs. Whilst Starter subscription to HE does not include membership of the Entrepreneurs Circle, you can qualify for preferential and exclusive joining fees, especially for the new Club Plus and Premier membership levels.</span></p>\r\n<h4>How this can help you</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Business strategy</li>\r\n<li>How to maximise you Marketing</li>\r\n<li>much much more</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>*NEW FOR AUGUST 2014*</h3>\r\n<p>See our Membership page to find out how you can join Nigels Entrepreneurs Circle and have automatic exclusive access to his <strong>Club Plus</strong> Membership for just 199 per month (usually 299 per month) and, even better still, the brand new <strong>Premier</strong> service, with expert marketers who will take care of ALL of your marketing for you. This is an additional marketing and business growth package that has been tailored to our industry.</p>\r\n<h3>ALL of your marketing, literally ALL ''Done-For-You'':</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Google Adwords </strong>set up and managed for you</li>\r\n<li><strong>Facebook Ads </strong>all set up and run for you</li>\r\n<li><strong>A brand new website </strong>with squeeze pages and ''lead magnets''</li>\r\n<li><strong>Auto-responder campaign</strong>, written and implemented</li>\r\n<li><strong>Direct mail</strong> pieces written, designed and sent out</li>\r\n<li><strong>Leaflets and flyers </strong>designed for you</li>\r\n<li><strong>Your existing database </strong>completely managed</li>\r\n<li><strong>Database built for you </strong>to turbo-charge your campaigns</li>\r\n<li><strong>All your marketing activity tracked </strong>using call numbers, cosmetic URLs etc, summarised in a monthly report so you can see exactly what''s happened and what the results are</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Too good to be true?</h3>\r\n<p>Well, just sign up to HE and then a member of the Entrepreneur''s Circle team will call you and tell you more!</p>'),
