(301, 19, 267, 'Bond Dickson', 'Cater Cost', 'Online recipe and menu costing', 'Catercost is a leading recipe costing and food profit calculator with nutritional info for caterers. Multi award winning licensee and trainer, Ali Carter set up Catercost to help the catering industry beat the statistics, take control and have a healthier business.\r\n\r\nHelping independent food operators squeeze every last drop of profit from their business and live the happy lives they deserve. Thats Catercosts mission.\r\n\r\nKnowing how hard it can be to know down to the last penny, the cost of the food you make and sell on your menu, this makes it easy, freeing you to cook while Catercost crunches your numbers!\r\n\r\nFeatures include:\r\n\r\n Cloud technology\r\n No software to download\r\n Recipe and menu creation\r\n Food profit calculator\r\n Nutritional information\r\n Supplier comparison on ingredients\r\n\r\nClub members of HE can have automatic use of Catercost, whilst Ali Carters sound and straight talking advice is available to all members.', 267, 'Say hello'),
(302, 20, 275, 'Bond Dickson', 'Entrepreneurs Circle', 'The UKs Largest Membership Organisation Dedicated to Helping Business Grow', 'In the last 8 years Nigel has built 8 separate 1m businesses from scratch, so he knows a thing or two about business growth. Nigels Entrepreneurs Circle is the UKs largest membership organisation dedicated to helping business grow. With a national network of over 50 Business Growth Advisors (BGAs), thousands of entrepreneurs have been helped by discovering new ideas and then making them work in their own businesses.\r\n\r\nAll Hospitality Entrepreneur members gain free marketing and business growth advice and tips from Nigel and his advisors, posted regularly on our website and blogs. Whilst Standard subscription to Hospitality Entrepreneur does not include membership of the Entrepreneurs Circle, you do qualify for a free 1:1 discussion with your local BGA.\r\n\r\nSee our Why Join? page to find out how you can join Nigels Entrepreneurs Circle and have automatic exclusive access to his Club Membership (usually 129 per month) and an additional marketing and business growth package that has been tailored to our industry for Club grade members.\r\nIn the last 8 years Nigel has built 8 separate 1m businesses from scratch, so he knows a thing or two about business growth. Nigels Entrepreneurs Circle is the UKs largest membership organisation dedicated to helping business grow. With a national network of over 50 Business Growth Advisors (BGAs), thousands of entrepreneurs have been helped by discovering new ideas and then making them work in their own businesses.\r\n\r\nAll Hospitality Entrepreneur members gain free marketing and business growth advice and tips from Nigel and his advisors, posted regularly on our website and blogs. Whilst Standard subscription to Hospitality Entrepreneur does not include membership of the Entrepreneurs Circle, you do qualify for a free 1:1 discussion with your local BGA.\r\n\r\nSee our Why Join? page to find 