(303, 19, 267, 'Bond Dickson', 'Pelican Procurement Services', 'Group purchasing power and efficiency through outourced procurement and invoice management ', 'By using Pelicans total collective purchasing volume of 140m, Hospitality Entrepreneur members are able to benefit from highly competitive trading arrangements with local and national suppliers, making substantial savings that would otherwise be unobtainable.\r\n\r\nWhilst saving money is one of the benefits of becoming an HE member, Pelican also offer unique additional services as part of our Food Profit Club, including regular impartial tendering on your behalf, centralised billing and co-ordination with Catercost and Innventive, to help ensure you have the best possible ongoing controls on your food costings and profits.\r\n\r\nPelican also lead the way in negotiating utility bills, chemicals, disposable, janitorial, credit & debit card processing and catering equipment. In fact, most areas of running a hospitality business!', 267, 'Say hello'),
(304, 19, 267, 'Bond Dickson', 'abv Training and Qualifications', 'A complete package of leading hospitality training throughout the UK.', 'ABV Training is an award winning company and leading provider of fun and effective personal license training (APLH (formerley NCPLH) & SCPLH ) and other BIIAB, HABC and CIEH qualifications at venues across the UK. Approved providers of the Apprenticeship in Licensed Hospitality for both Level 2 and 3, they also offer a wide range of affordable e-courses suitable for consistent induction and compliance training.\r\n\r\nRecognised as one of the very top training providers, they work for many of the UK''s leading operators in pubs, hotels and leisure offering bespoke courses tailored to meet business needs. David and Frazer and their team based across the country offer such a comprehensive training solution that it would have been crazy not to have teamed up with Hospitality Entrepreneur, to provide you and your staff team with all the back up and qualifications you need! ', 267, 'Say hello'),
(305, 21, 267, 'Bond Dickson', 'Botti Creative', 'Marketing Driven Design', 'You can have the best looking website in the world, but if it doesn''t bring in new business, its about as much use as a glass cricket bat.\r\n\r\nAt Botti Creative, our experienced team of design experts know everything there is to know about building websites that not only make the internet a slightly prettier place to be, but do a fantastic job when it comes to converting visits into cash.\r\n\r\nDo you have a database packed full of customers or potential clients sat waiting for you to tell them about your exciting new product? If the answer''s a big fat NO we can help!\r\n\r\nAt Botti Creative we''re masters at email marketing and all that it entails. From capturing and building your database to handling autoresponders and full email campaigns, we''ve got it covered!', 277, 'Say hello'),
