(1087, 169, 267, 'Pelican Procurement Services', 'Pelican Procurement Services', 'Group purchasing power and efficiency through outourced procurement and invoice management ', 'By using Pelicans total collective purchasing volume of 140m, Hospitality Entrepreneur members are able to benefit from highly competitive trading arrangements with local and national suppliers, making substantial savings that would otherwise be unobtainable.', 300, 'Say hello'),
