(1125, 74, 275, 'Bond Dickson', 'Bramble Buzz', 'Social Media expertise from Julia Bramble  The UK Entrepreneurs Social Media Expert', 'Julia has a sound conviction that through social media, hospitality businesses have access to hundreds of thousands of people, all of whom might be interested, in some way, in your business. She helps you channel that power, so that you can do it right and get the results you want and need for your business. She fervently believes that every single business owner should be using social media  that they should not be intimidated by it, or be put off by horror stories about how long it all takes.\r\n\r\n', 275, 'View Partner'),
