(1, 'Welcome to concrete5 - an Open Source CMS Sidebar  Everything about concrete5 is completely customizable through the CMS. This is a separate area from the main content on the homepage. You can drag and drop blocks like this around your layout.  Welcome to concrete5!\n                                         Content Management is easy with concrete5''s in-context editing. Just login and you can change things as you browse your site. \n                                         You can watch videos and learn how to: \n                                        \n                                        Edit this page.\n                                        Add a new page.\n                                        Add some basic functionality, like a Form.\n                                        Finding & adding more functionality and themes.\n                                        \n                                         We''ve taken the liberty to build out the rest of this site with some sample content that will help you learn concrete5. Wander around a bit, or click Dashboard to get to the Sitemap and quickly delete the parts you don''t want.  \r\n                	Features\r\n                    Exclusive VIP joining discountwith 30% off annual starter membership available\r\n                    24/7 unlimited access to all downloadable member advice and business resources, updated monthly\r\n                    Your own confidential Business HealthCheck questionnaire\r\n                    Free membership of HE Buying Group (administered through Pelican Purchasing), giving you access to national scale discounts on food, drink, consumables and utilities.\r\n                    Members Only business building blogs and marketing nuggets from Peter Austen and Ali Carter\r\n                    Hospitality Entrepreneur circular,posted and online\r\n                    \r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n           \r\n                \r\n                \r\n\r\n                \r\n                 Level\r\n                 Level\r\n                 Level\r\n                \r\n                \r\n                 \r\n                 \r\n                 \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                 \r\n                 \r\n                 \r\n                \r\n     			\r\n                 \r\n                 \r\n                 \r\n                \r\n       			\r\n                 \r\n                 \r\n                 \r\n                \r\n     			\r\n                 \r\n                 \r\n                 \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n                \r\n          \r\n         \r\n                      Andrew and Claire Bowen - Oxford and Abingdon - Java & Co - We joined Hospitality Entrepreneur in November 2013 and the benefits of being members have been truly ''business changing'' already. - Having a 24/7 expert resource and access to industry leading Partner businesses has transformed the way we operate, instantly improving gross profits, saving us loads of time each week and could ultimately increase the value of our business by as much as 200,000 within 12 months. Not bad for an initial investment of just 10 a month! After 6 years in business, the future suddenly looks good." Watch this month''s exclusive ''Success Secrets'' videos\r\n\r\n Take your  FREE 30 DAY TRIAL of Hospitality Entrepreneur (''HE''), if you''re an owner of any independent hospitality business who really wants to thrive NOW, without the usual growing pains \r\n\r\n\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n  \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n    Latest From The HE Blog  Exclusive ''HE'' video interviews with Alex Reilley \r\n Part 1 - an introduction to the Loungers concept - the 75 million ''Happy Accident'' - Loungers'' future  HE ''Success Secrets'' videos\r\n Convenient, educational and inspirational. Each month we interview some of the top UK hospitality entrepreneurs.  Regular Great Content\r\nWe bring you regular helpful content from the hospitality world. Downloadable content, blog posts and insider videos from some of the most success full hospitality entrepreneur''s.  Simple, smart and sustainable business growth ''secrets'', every month\r\nDo you want to expand your business, but don''t know how?\r\nDoes your business control you, rather than the other way round?\r\nDo you want to know which changes could double your annual profits?\r\nCould you control your business by delegating and outsourcing more effectively?\r\n   \r\nWell, GOOD NEWS!, because Hospitality Entrepreneur (''HE'') provides answers to all the above. We''re a bit like having your own personal industry expert with you full time, but a lot less boring and without having to pay the expensive day rate. The result of a ground breaking new collaboration of proven industry experts and companies, we really can (and DO!) ensure you get better profits, better knowledge and better peace of mind. \r\nHere''s what we''ve got for you:\r\n\r\n\r\n24/7 advice, guidance, systems and success ''secrets'' at your fingertips, from the most successful entrepreneurs and hospitality business owners, just like you\r\ninspiration, exclusive insights, practical help, templates and resources, released and updated every month\r\na revolutionary ''done for you'' marketing support package\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\na real chance to control and grow your business before it controls you\r\nyears of combined knowledge, experience and systems gift-wrapped for you\r\n1:1 mentoring from real people, not just our website!\r\n\r\n  Who''s involved?\r\nWe can bring you a unique collaboration, with unrivalled experience and expertise in supplying and actually running profitable hospitality businesses. Our contributors and Partners are driven by a shared vision for providing increased profitability, knowledge and peace of mind for our members. \r\nLike you, we''ve also experienced the sleepless nights worrying about staff, premises and bills that need paying yesterday. So why not let us share our advice with you, especially as we''ve had our fair share of celebrations, financial successes and Champagne popping also!Meet Our Partners  September members'' benefits:\r\n\r\nNEW revolutionary Club Plus andPremier''done for you'' marketing package\r\nNEW exclusive member-only resources ready to help you grow your business\r\nNEW HE video Part 2 with Alex Reilley, MD Lounges and Cosy Clubs\r\n ', 'Home', '', NULL, '2012-01-24 10:10:24', '2014-09-07 17:31:40', NULL, 0),
