(118, 'About Us  \r\nOur Guarantees To You\r\n We can guarantee that you''ll find the information, resources and advice incredibly inspirational, practical and easy to implement. No waffle, useless theory or rhetoric, just pratical tried and tested solutions or cutting edge ideas. \r\n For your FREE TRIAL Starter membership, if you don''t want to start paying just 10 a month after 30 days and don''t feel that ongoing membership will benefit your business, then fine, just tell us before the end of your 30 day FREE TRIAL and we''ll cancel your ongoing subscription. No questions asked, we won''t charge you a penny. \r\n For more serious entrepreneurs, we recognise your investment, time and involvement, so the guarantees are even stronger. If for some reason the HE website or our Partner businesses do not live up to our promises or Code of Conduct, then contact us within 30 days telling us where we went wrong and we will actually refund your first month''s subscription to that level of membership. \r\n  We Don''t Just Waffle About Hospitality Entrepreneurship...\r\n  \r\n\r\n We approach hospitality from a unique perspective. We all know that the challenges and demands of owning and running a restaurant, pub, bar, caf or hotel can be extreme, so extreme that the business usually ends up controlling you, preventing you from realising your goals and ambitions. So, since the 1990''s and even more since 2001 we''ve been travelling the ''new'' world of hospitality, learning it, practising it and teaching it like no one else. \r\n The result is Hospitality Entrepreneur (HE) a new ''Go to'' information and advice website, a members'' ''Club'' and above all a ''get down and dirty'' practical service for smart hospitality business owners. No bland corporate waffle here, created just to fill up a company webpage. Instead, valuable information, success secrets from those at the top of the hospitality tree and exclusive access to services and systems that we consider to be the best way to grow a solid business. \r\nOur mission will never change. We ensure that you get: \r\n\r\n\r\nBetter profits\r\nBetter knowledge\r\nBetter peace of mind\r\n\r\nHow do we do this?\r\n ''HE'' founder Peter Austen has been in the business of performance coaching for hundreds of hospitality businesses since 1993, before anyone used that term. We hate to boast, but today we are a collaboration of leading industry professionals and companies, with thousands of happy clients and unrivalled expertise in building and running successful hospitality businesses. \r\n Every month we will release the best and latest industry advice (see Resources) to our members. This will be available for your use as and when you want it, 24/7, ready for you and your staff to implement straight away in your business.   In addition to the best business advice, our members also enjoy privileged direct access to our Partner business services.   \r\n\r\nDo you want to expand your business but dont quite know how? \r\nWould you like to radically increase your businesss profits whilst decreasing its reliance on YOU?\r\nDoes your business control you, rather than the other way around?\r\n\r\n If you feel the answer to any of these questions is ''YES'', then you are almost certainly a hospitality entrepreneur, so take the FREE TRIAL and join our Club today! \r\n So, who is Peter Austen?\r\n  \r\nHospitality Entrepreneur (HE) was founded in July 2013 by Peter Austen. Peter is MD of the hospitality operations consultants Innventive, having spent the last 20 years immersed in hospitality business coaching and operating pubs, restaurants, bars and hotels himself. \r\nFind out more about Peter \r\n   \r\nJoin Today\r\n Join today, either by taking advantage of our Starter membership 30 day FREE trial or, if you''ve been lucky enough to have been contacted by one of our Partner businesses, using your exclusive VIP Launch Offer. \r\nStarter membership - 30 day FREE trial\r\n Dip your toe in, receive a FREE copy of the 245 page ''Botty''s Rules'', enjoy access to 70% of the HE website and resources, as well as privileged access to our Partner business services  \r\nExclusive VIP Launch Offer\r\n Our VIP Launch Offer, including 3 months extra subscription for FREE, is available to friends of our Partner businesses and those of you who complete our 2 minute survey when you take out annual subscription \r\nEither way, join the HE Club now and start to:\r\n\r\nAttract and KEEP more customers\r\nIncrease your bottom line profits\r\nAccess exclusive member business resources 24/7\r\nAccess easy-to-implement business growth secrets\r\nBenefit from the latest purchasing, marketing, training, food costing and operations support\r\nStart implementing and benefitting, or your money back\r\n\r\nIt''s all here for as little as 10 (plus VAT) per month\r\n  Videos, articles, blogs, checklists and numerous trade secrets\r\n  \r\n   \r\n A sprinkling of the hottest advice and help is provided by our assortment of writers and business experts. \r\n Insight and inspiration is provided by one of the countrys best known serial entrepreneurs, Nigel Botterill. He knows a fair bit about starting, expanding and selling multi-million pound businesses, having done that himself from scratch eight (at the last count!) times in the last ten years. \r\n Practical operational advice, including checklists, templates and behind the scenes insights, is also provided by Peter Austen and Ali Carter, who have all the war stories and overview necessary after owning and running a variety of super-successful restaurants, hotels, pubs and bars themselves.  ', 'Why Join?', '', '/about', '2012-01-24 10:10:00', '2014-09-01 13:38:18', NULL, 0),
